metadata.name: SHANI
metadata.description:
LAZERGIRLS of the "Other World".

You know your hood, where to find the snacks, the entertainment the nightlife. The night is young, let's have some fun and check the clubs. Will the famous dancers have performances tonight?

---

The beats are pumping. No one, really no one stands or sits still anymore. The music is dark, electronic and the bass is so strong that you can feel it in your heart. Shani is on stage, she is the number ONE of the "Other World", there is no better pole dancer.  She always has her own outfits at the start and they are just terrific.

---

LAZERGIRLS is a project based on inspiration from Cyberpunk, Shadowrun, electronic music like Laserkraft, and much more. 
Dedicated to the neon dancers in nightclubs and holographic projections.
